  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382100/extras/71093831778814f0ce5b4700b73e0c2a.poster.avif?t=1742152207\" width=800 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382100/extras/71093831778814f0ce5b4700b73e0c2a.webm?t=1742152207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382100/extras/71093831778814f0ce5b4700b73e0c2a.mp4?t=1742152207\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >        Wanme Times – the ever-evolving game workshop! We create games with creativity and passion, constantly updating the levels of The “POCKET ORACLE”, enhancing the fun, building a rich game ecosystem, and providing a lasting gaming experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >            POCKET ORACLE – Useful every day, foreseeing a different kind of excitement!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382100/extras/72b5f246d5ca91ca8863603da9145a8c.avif?t=1742152207\" width=630 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                 Explore the Wisdom of the 64 Hexagrams</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >         Inspired by Taoist philosophy and the I Ching, *POCKET ORACLE* is an interactive divination game that offers easy-to-understand insights. Unlock the meanings of 64 hexagrams and gain valuablea guidance on love, career, health, and wealth—shaping your journey with every choice you make.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382100/extras/0ec565f3a7f9b5da55df246a7bc3cc8e.avif?t=1742152207\" width=630 height=122 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >         Talk to your personal guide NPC, \"Fuxi,\" who will interpret the hexagrams and provide insightful, practical advice.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >        Unlock prophecies through tasks. Your choices shape your destiny, and the power to change your future is in your hands!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382100/extras/f2a06ebfdad7fc2bd42bf38facd244bf.poster.avif?t=1742152207\" width=630 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382100/extras/f2a06ebfdad7fc2bd42bf38facd244bf.webm?t=1742152207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382100/extras/f2a06ebfdad7fc2bd42bf38facd244bf.mp4?t=1742152207\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382100/extras/2621c65e0297c257a92a19832076435c.avif?t=1742152207\" width=630 height=122 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >         Immerse yourself in a beautiful world inspired by Eastern aesthetics, where ethereal music amplifies the sense of mystery.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382100/extras/2a039d8e0687ae5a02a2b4a9657d05c9.poster.avif?t=1742152207\" width=800 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382100/extras/2a039d8e0687ae5a02a2b4a9657d05c9.webm?t=1742152207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382100/extras/2a039d8e0687ae5a02a2b4a9657d05c9.mp4?t=1742152207\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382100/extras/9c4fa5f04f82e88c1df8726a46d5a02b.avif?t=1742152207\" width=630 height=122 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >           Complete six mini-tasks to uncover the mysteries of life and gain deeper insights into love, career, health, wealth, and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382100/extras/066f718706511301b283b8aae28bec1f.poster.avif?t=1742152207\" width=800 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382100/extras/066f718706511301b283b8aae28bec1f.webm?t=1742152207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382100/extras/066f718706511301b283b8aae28bec1f.mp4?t=1742152207\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382100/extras/3623b359fd37c499f793faf618ba09ac.avif?t=1742152207\" width=630 height=122 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >            Can you change your destiny? Will you face the uncertainties of the future? Download now and start your journey!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382100/extras/67306577756cf782f9f139027e652b63.poster.avif?t=1742152207\" width=800 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382100/extras/67306577756cf782f9f139027e652b63.webm?t=1742152207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382100/extras/67306577756cf782f9f139027e652b63.mp4?t=1742152207\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Some prop designs and background creations in this game are generated by AI intelligence, giving players a unique visual experience.\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
